title: High Gold JG main LF team / duo

embed.description: Oobskies / Gold 2 46LP / 127W 118L Win Ratio 52% / Udyr - 54W 36L Win Ratio 60%, Vi - 17W 17L Win Ratio 50%, Shyvana - 20W 10L Win Ratio 67%, Kayn - 10W 14L Win Ratio 42%, Shaco - 6W 5L Win Ratio 55%

body:
Hi,
I have been playing since S4 as a Jg main.  Currently G2 and aiming to see how high into plat I can get this season in solo Q .
I am interested in joining a team for some co-ordinated 5v5 games.  I have a quality Mike and discord and will be vocal.  I can play a variety of champs and styles and am willing to learn new champs to suit team style.  I can play from 7-7:30pm to 11pm on all nights except Tues.
Also interested in playing Duo with competent players to climb in solo Q.
If interested add me in game.
p.s I'm 34 and would prefer to play with adults.
